heading: Bloodsoaked Crag Dungeon Guide
content: Bloodsoaked Crag is a long and winding dungeon that has backtracking, the dangerous stun-happy Cannibals, and the . It might be worth completion for it's first time rewards, but otherwise, I'd avoid this dungeon. While every dungeon has a somewhat randomized layout, there are patterns to where objectives and bosses are located. This map will help you identify those layouts so you can complete dungeons faster and maximize your XP and loot per hour! Reviewed by
